Usage: ON [#|+|-|^|&|@]WINDOW_CHANGE [-|^]<parameters> [action]
  Whenever a window is swapped, this hook is triggered
    $0    Refnum or name of the window we came from
    $1    Refnum or name of the window we swapped to
